text.tspan: Also, those well-suited to self-study methods have not found any change in stress levels due to
the lockdown. Unfortunately, a large proportion of Indian students do not have access to online
means of learning. With schools closed for an elongated period of time, even after the relaxation
of the lockdown, the uncertainty regarding school examinations and university entrance
examinations, has left the student body uneasy with added academic pressure.
